# Linux Notes

This repository contains my personal Linux notes created while studying cybersecurity.

The purpose of this repository is to document Linux commands, concepts, and practical examples as I continue developing my skills through self-study, TryHackMe, Microsoft Learn, and my IT Security Analyst education.

## Topics

* Navigation
* File & Directory Management
* Searching
* Permissions
* Networking
* Package Management
* Bash
* Security Commands

## Goal

This repository will continue to grow as I learn new Linux concepts and improve my practical skills.
